## 🐛 Bug Report

I generated some excel files with this library https://www.nuget.org/packages/MiniExcel#versions-body-tab. I am trying to read the excel file and I got an error: 

Cannot set properties of undefined (setting 'sheetNo')

Lib version: 4.3.0

## Steps To Reproduce

Try to open a excel file generated with external library.

```javascript
`workbook.xlsx.readFile(pathFile).then(function () {
            const headers: string[] = [];
            const sheet = workbook.getWorksheet(sheetNumber);
            for (let index = 1; index <= totalColumns; index++) {
                headers.push(sheet.getRow(1).getCell(index).text);
            }
            return headers;`
```

## The expected behaviour:

Open the excel file


## Possible solution (optional, but very helpful):
